1. Make a folder, can be named anything.
2. Download the 3 files https://github.com/cr3cked/CR3CK/blob/main/discord.vbs https://github.com/cr3cked/CR3CK/blob/main/READ%20ME.txt https://github.com/cr3cked/CR3CK/blob/main/PixelGunCheat.dll (first 2 are optional, only the .dll and injector are needed)
3. Download the injector
Unzipped: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1X_Q6tK5c5ZSjzJeotBf5TnEspaCcCqg2/view?usp=drive_link 
Zipped: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1xGW4DDPOVyHW1bvU_RG1sNtVF3qNAcjI/view?usp=drive_link
4. Enter Pixel Gun 3D
5. Open the injector, sometimes it may crash
6. DO NOT SPEND MORE THAN 12,000 COINS OR GEMS A DAY OR YOUR ACCOUNT IS AT HIGH RISK OF BAN
7. Use right-shift to toggle GUI
8. https://discord.gg/HAbvvM3xe9 Join the discord
